{"tid":1963324,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"香港與台灣更像同盟 中獨份子哭成淚人 港台更像一家人 不用分裂","createTime":"2020-04-08T05:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T08:34:16.000Z","uid":5205,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3440bbd81cb5a7d1c1e0d8f7d3155e5eef2cecec","tid":1963324,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:14:22.000Z","msg":"香港人與台灣人 友好 更甚於中國<br />\n<br />\n台灣 香港 支持民主自由 都已經是一家人<br />\n<br />\n誰還會跳到 中國 裡面 做一家人<br />\n<br />\n所以中國是中獨份子 <br />\n分裂了香港同台灣的感情<br />\n<br />\n中國人必須維護 香港和台灣不可分割的友好關係<br />\n中獨份子 不得嚴重 干預亞洲太平洋區的領土安全"},{"pid":"1901a214319d2a24e70fa38a66ea2da65b17c342","tid":1963324,"uid":89131,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"台灣政權先係正統政權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b2db934d6af1c4102d16647fa560c37706a156","tid":1963324,"uid":258706,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:24:47.000Z","msg":"一個中國<br />\n中華民國<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d270a39362644e0b8084389ce5309214c51dc8ee","tid":1963324,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"中獨份子 不要離間 香港和台灣的正統中國 (可稱台灣國)"},{"pid":"e9f025752f8da8b79af13f514ee1fcd43b53ae3e","tid":1963324,"uid":214036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:57:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"674d7554f3a55ca492569ffd13c768b132f80df6","tid":1963324,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T05:58:31.000Z","msg":"正，推"},{"pid":"ffe8a1b0f80638c71eb2b63e1fae5f8a02e3c92e","tid":1963324,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e9f025752f8da8b79af13f514ee1fcd43b53ae3e","tid":1963324,"uid":214036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d270a39362644e0b8084389ce5309214c51dc8ee","tid":1963324,"uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-0